# DevSecOps

Owners: DevSecOps Engineer, Cloud Security Controls Engineer, Software Supply Chain Security Engineer.

Cover pipeline security, IAM, workload identity, secrets management patterns, SAST, DAST, SCA, IaC/container/Kubernetes scanning design, policy as code, OPA, Gatekeeper, Kyverno, SBOM, signing strategy, provenance, SLSA-aligned controls, and remediation routing.

Use `.cursor/skills/devsecops/SKILL.md` and `docs/devsecops-workflows.md`.

DevSecOps does not own pentesting, SOC/SIEM, threat intelligence, forensics, enterprise GRC, or general security incident response.

Stop on requested scanner execution, signing, secret-store access, enforcement, pipeline blocking, cloud/security mutation, Cybersecurity-owned work, real identifiers, or missing human approval.
